This is a formatting standard for this project.
Checking using cpplint.py from https://github.com/google/styleguide/tree/gh-pages/cpplint
$ cpplint.py --filter=-whitespace/line_length,-build/include,-legal/copyright,-readability/streams *.cc *.h 

Automatic Formatting using astyle from http://astyle.sourceforge.net/
$ astyle --project=.astylerc *.cc *.h
